normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然而家又繼續毒番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5aca01fb66c5e7a2f666a6bcadf69bab777c62","tid":128421,"uid":76242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T00:11:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>廿年姐屌</blockquote><br />\n人生有幾多個廿年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n廿歲仔無拍過拖好正常姐,我都毒左廿二年先開齋,初試性感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然而家又繼續毒番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好容易將感情撈亂，人地對我好，就想發展成愛情（不分男女），但自己又唔會開口。"},{"pid":"5318cfda6fdd54cf1553b2f2abe7ceb2af2b378f","tid":128421,"uid":48211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T00:17:10.000Z","msg":"毒成點？"},{"pid":"f5a2846aad6ca41a037152f1d7b5549b5807b26c","tid":128421,"uid":76242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T09:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒成點？</blockquote><br />\n討厭行街 可以幾個月都唔出家門口<br />\n住了十幾年既地方 附近有咩都唔知道<br />\n或者咁講除了地鐵/巴士總站返屋企既路之外其他地方都未去過。"},{"pid":"cc64dc95e8e6e6f0f7e5888a9c3c778aa58b77e0","tid":128421,"uid":76242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T19:49:33.000Z","msg":"想脫毒"}]}